title: Bakers Delight - Bayside Shopping Centre
description: Bakery chain, offering numerous savory and sweet vegan items. Products that are vegan suitable are clearly notated on its website. In store a till docket can be requested for each product that lists all of the ingredients as well as "suitable for vegans" if that is the case.
streetAddress: Shop Go16B, Bayside Shopping Centre, 2 Olsen St
